    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Peeſeen tohs pee taweem\nPirfſteem / rakſti tohs us to\nGaidu tawas Sirđs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Safti us to Gudribu:\nTu eſti manna Mahfa/ un to\nSapratchanu fanz par tawu fi teew faſtapt/ tawu Waigu tik-\nklahteju Raddu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Ka winna tevis paſarga\nno Zitta Seewas/ no tahs Swe-\nſchincezes/ kas mihtus Wahrdus\ndohd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Jo zaur manna Namma\nLohgu/ zaur manneem Skadri-\nxeem es ſkattijohs/ un redseju\nſtarp teem Neprattigeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Es nomanniju ſtarp teem\nBehrneem weenu besprahtignu\nfannekſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Tas gabje fezzen us to Ge-\nlufahnis winna Stuhri/ un ſtaı-\ngaja us to Zeltu pee winnas\nNamma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Nowakkarôs / Deenas\nWakkarâ/ tumſchâ Nakti/ un\nTumſtibâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un redſi/ weena Secwa\nfaſtappe winnam Mankas Gehr-\nbuma/ nn ar * wiltigu Sirđt.\nEebr: Wall: Kas fawu Širdi apfargajiſi, tas\nirr: jepſchu winna Zittam to Širdi lohg un\nagmahne, tarſchu winna fawâ Širdi flepeni\nween ruurahs, un us Wiltu dohina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Scht bija trakka un ne-\nturriga/ winnas Kabjas ne pa-\nlikke fawâ Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Drihs irr winna ahra/\nDrihs us Eelahm/ un gluhe pee\nwiſſahm Stuhreim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Un ta apkampe winnu/\nan ſkuhpſtija winnu/ rundsijahs\nbeſtaunigt/ un ſazzija us winnu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Es eſimu Pateizibas-Up-\npurus mannis pehz uppurejſi/\nes eſimu ſchodcen fawu Apfohli-\nſchann nomakſajſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Tadeht eſimu es iſgahjn-\nkuschi mekleht/ un eſimu teew at-\nradduft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Es eſmu fawu Gultu ar\nGardinehn iſgresnojuti ar iſgree-\nſahm (Kohfu) Bildehn/ ar\ndahrgu Andeklu no Egiptes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Es eſmu fawu Gultu\niſkwehpinaſſi ar Mirrehm/ Aloë\nun Kanneeleeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Nahz/ lai mehs papillam\nKahribu dsennam lihds Rihtam/\nlai mehs Mihleſtibaâ lihgſmoja-\nmees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Jo mans Wihrs newaid\nMahjäs/ wiſsch irr tahtu Zeltu\naiſgahjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Wiſsch irr to Randas\nMakku lihdsi nehints/ Sweht-\nfös wiſsch attat nahks jawas\nMahjäs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Winna nowehrſe to ar\nfawu leeku Wallohu/ winna no-\nwaddija to ar jawo Luhpo Lip-\nubu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Tas gabje winnat ahtri\npakkat/ itt ka weens Wehrſis pee\nRauschanas ect/ un itt ka us\nSeektu / kur tee Šekki tohp\npahrmahziti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Kaineht ta Bulta winna\nAkurs pahrfchkehle / ka lahds\nPut-\n"
    }
  ],
